user launches game + standard game config 			          - ship is created 						          - only one ship is on screen
user launches game + 100% ship creation is set in config 	- 10 ships are created 						      - only 10 ships are on screen
user launches game + -10% ship creation is set in config 	- exception is thrown 						      - game displays error for config being incorrect
config error is displayed 					                      - config is repaired to standard 				- game launches with no config error

game is running + user clicks any other input 			- non registered input 						- no missiles are shown or created

user clicks spacebar 						- missile generated 						- missile shown on screen
user clicks right click 				- missile generated 						- missile shown on screen
user click any other input			- invalid input							    - no missile is shown on screen

user launched missile (spacebar) 				          - missile is launched 						- missile launches from bottom center of screen
user launched missile (spacebar + any input) 			- missile is launched 						- missile launches from bottom center of screen
user launched missile (right click) 				      - missile is launched 						- missile launches and keeps persistent movement
user launched missile (right click + any input) 	- missile is launched 						- missile launches and keeps persistent movement


5 missiles on screen 						- user spawns another missile (spacebar)			            - the new missile does not get created
5 missiles on screen 						- user spawns another missile (spacebar + any input)		  - the new missile does not get created
5 missiles on screen 						- user spawns another missile (right click) 			        - the new missile does not get created
5 missiles on screen 						- user spawns another missile (right click + any input) 	- the new missile does not get created
5 missiles on screen 						- user spawns another missile (spacebar + right click)		- the new missile does not get created

missile is launched 						- missile goes off screen 					- missile gets removed

(cascading tests)
missile and ship are on screen 					      - missile and ship intersect (same coords) 			- hit detected
hit detected 							                    - ship and missile are removed 					        - ship and missile are not on screen
missile and ship are removed due to hit 			- trigger explosion animation 					        - explosion animation is on screen
missile and ship intersect 					          - hit detected 							                    - hit count incremented

